snippet.title: Johnny Depp | Amber Heard Spotted Heavily Bruised Forearm Arriving LA...
snippet.description:

Amber Heard Spotted Heavily Bruised Forearm Arriving LA Bitter Battle Ex Johnny Depp Rages Following Shock Video Release.
Amber Heard is spotted with heavily bruised forearm while arriving in LA as bitter battle with ex Johnny Depp rages following shock video release

Amber Heard was seen arriving in Los Angeles on Friday with a host of painful-looking red marks along the length of her forearm. 
The actress' return to LA from London comes after she denied leaking a video in which her estranged husband Johnny Depp is seen hurling a glass and wine bottle across their kitchen. 
TMZ report the actress has issued a statement clarifying her position regarding the controversial tape while revealing she ‘underestimated’ the emotional impact divorce proceedings against the Hollywood star would have on her.
